---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Catalyst Neuromorphic" description="Building neuromorphic processors to challenge the way intelligence is computed." hasFog={true}>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="pt-36 pb-16 px-6 md:px-12" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div style="max-width:700px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center;">
      <p class="text-sm text-catalyst-blue font-medium tracking-wider uppercase mb-5">About</p>
      <h1 style="font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif; font-size:clamp(2.6rem,5.5vw,4.2rem); font-weight:700; letter-spacing:-0.04em; line-height:1;">
        AI has a hardware problem.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-base text-white/35 mt-5" style="line-height:1.7;">We're building the processors to fix it.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THE PROBLEM -->
  <section class="pb-24 px-6 md:px-12" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div style="max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;">
      <div class="card-glass reveal" style="padding:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);">
        <div style="position:relative;z-index:2;">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold tracking-tight mb-4">The scaling wall</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-white/40" style="line-height:1.75;">
            <p>Modern AI runs on hardware that was never designed for intelligence. GPUs burn hundreds of watts per chip. Data centres already consume over 2% of global electricity, and that share is climbing fast. Training a single large language model can use more energy than a hundred homes do in a year. The models are getting bigger, but the returns are shrinking.</p>
            <p>And for all that power, these systems still can't learn from new information without being retrained from scratch. They can't run without a data centre. They can't operate without sending your data to someone else's infrastructure.</p>
            <p>The human brain does all of this on 20 watts. It learns continuously. It processes information in real-time. It runs at the edge, on-device, with no internet connection required. The gap between biological intelligence and artificial intelligence isn't a software problem. It's a hardware problem.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DIVIDER -->
  <div style="width:100%;max-width:400px;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,rgba(59,130,246,0.2),transparent);margin:0 auto;"></div>

  <!-- WHAT WE'RE BUILDING -->
  <section class="py-24 px-6 md:px-12" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div style="max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;">
      <h2 class="reveal text-[clamp(1.8rem,3vw,2.4rem)] font-bold tracking-tight mb-6" style="font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;">Neuromorphic processors.</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-white/40 reveal" style="line-height:1.75;">
        <p>Neuromorphic chips compute the way neurons do. They're event-driven &mdash; they only consume energy when there's something to process. They can learn on the hardware itself, not just run pre-trained models. They operate at the edge, on-device, without cloud dependency. And they do it at a fraction of the power cost.</p>
        <p>This technology exists. Intel has Loihi. IBM built TrueNorth. But both are closed, corporate, and inaccessible. If you're not inside those companies or their select research programmes, you don't get access. The hardware that could reshape computing is locked behind walls.</p>
        <p>Catalyst is building the open alternative. Full processor designs, published research, and a cloud platform anyone can use today. We're not asking for permission to compete with billion-dollar companies. We're just doing it.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DIVIDER -->
  <div style="width:100%;max-width:400px;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,rgba(59,130,246,0.2),transparent);margin:0 auto;"></div>

  <!-- WHERE WE ARE -->
  <section class="py-24 px-6 md:px-12" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div style="max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;">
      <h2 class="reveal text-[clamp(1.8rem,3vw,2.4rem)] font-bold tracking-tight mb-6" style="font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;">Where we are.</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-white/40 reveal" style="line-height:1.75;">
        <p>We're early. Three processor generations are designed, built in software, and validated on real hardware. Two have published papers you can read today, with the third coming soon. A cloud API is live &mdash; you can run a neuromorphic network right now, without buying anything.</p>
        <p>We're raising funding and building toward manufactured silicon. That's the goal: a physical chip you can hold, running real neuromorphic intelligence. We're not there yet. But the architecture is complete, tested, and protected by patent.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DIVIDER -->
  <div style="width:100%;max-width:400px;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,rgba(59,130,246,0.2),transparent);margin:0 auto;"></div>

  <!-- FOUNDER -->
  <section class="py-24 px-6 md:px-12" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div style="max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;">
      <h2 class="reveal text-[clamp(1.8rem,3vw,2.4rem)] font-bold tracking-tight mb-6" style="font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;">Founder.</h2>
      <div class="reveal card-glass" style="padding:clamp(1.5rem,3vw,2rem);">
        <div class="text-sm text-white/40" style="line-height:1.75;position:relative;z-index:2;">
          <p><strong class="text-white/70">Henry Shulayev Barnes</strong> &mdash; engineering student at the University of Aberdeen. Started Catalyst because the neuromorphic hardware that should exist doesn't, and the hardware that does exist isn't accessible. Currently a member of Techscaler, Scotland's tech startup community.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DIVIDER -->
  <div style="width:100%;max-width:400px;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,rgba(59,130,246,0.2),transparent);margin:0 auto;"></div>

  <!-- WHY TRUST US -->
  <section class="py-24 px-6 md:px-12" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div style="max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;">
      <h2 class="reveal text-[clamp(1.8rem,3vw,2.4rem)] font-bold tracking-tight mb-6" style="font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;">Don't take our word for it.</h2>
      <div class="reveal grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        {[
          { title: 'Read the papers', desc: 'Published papers on Zenodo with DOIs. Open access. Every claim documented.' },
          { title: 'Try the cloud', desc: 'The API is live. Run a neuromorphic network from your terminal. Free tier available.' },
          { title: 'Check the hardware', desc: 'Our designs run on real FPGA boards, not just simulators. Physical silicon execution.' },
          { title: 'Join the community', desc: 'Open GitHub, public research, growing backers. We build in the open.' },
        ].map(item => (
          <div class="card-glass" style="padding:1.25rem 1.5rem;">
            <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white/75 mb-1.5" style="position:relative;z-index:2;">{item.title}</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-white/30" style="line-height:1.6;position:relative;z-index:2;">{item.desc}</div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- IP -->
  <section class="py-16 px-6 md:px-12" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div style="max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;">
      <div class="reveal card-glass" style="padding:clamp(1.5rem,3vw,2rem);">
        <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:auto 1fr;gap:0.6rem 2rem;position:relative;z-index:2;">
          {[
            ['UK Patents', 'Filed February 2026'],
            ['RTL', 'BSL 1.1 — proprietary'],
            ['SDK', 'BSL 1.1'],
            ['Papers', 'Open access on Zenodo'],
            ['API Client', 'MIT — open source'],
          ].map(([label, value]) => (
            <>
              <div class="text-sm text-white/30">{label}</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-white/50">{value}</div>
            </>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- GET IN TOUCH — exact homepage section -->
  <section class="connect-section" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <h2 style="font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif; font-size:clamp(2.4rem,5vw,3.6rem); font-weight:700; letter-spacing:-0.035em; line-height:1.08; text-align:center; margin-bottom:18px;">Get in touch.</h2>
    <p class="connect-email"><a href="mailto:henry@catalyst-neuromorphic.com">henry@catalyst-neuromorphic.com</a></p>
    <div class="connect-grid">
      <a href="https://github.com/catalyst-neuromorphic" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="connect-card">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M15 22v-4a4.8 4.8 0 0 0-1-3.5c3 0 6-2 6-5.5.08-1.25-.27-2.48-1-3.5.28-1.15.28-2.35 0-3.5 0 0-1 0-3 1.5-2.64-.5-5.36-.5-8 0C6 2 5 2 5 2c-.3 1.15-.3 2.35 0 3.5A5.4 5.4 0 0 0 4 9c0 3.5 3 5.5 6 5.5-.39.49-.68 1.05-.85 1.65S8.93 17.38 9 18v4"/><path d="M9 18c-4.51 2-5-2-7-2"/></svg>
        <span class="connect-label">GitHub</span>
        <span class="connect-sub">Source & contributions</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/research" class="connect-card">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/></svg>
        <span class="connect-label">Research</span>
        <span class="connect-sub">Papers & benchmarks</span>
      </a>
      <a href="https://ko-fi.com/catalystneuromorphic" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="connect-card">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/></svg>
        <span class="connect-label">Support</span>
        <span class="connect-sub">Buy us a coffee on Ko-Fi</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style is:global>
    /* Connect section (homepage exact code) */
    .connect-section {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 80px 32px 100px;
    }
    .connect-email {
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 56px;
    }
    .connect-email a {
      color: rgba(59,130,246,0.8);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }
    .connect-email a:hover { color: #60A5FA; }
    .connect-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .connect-card {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 36px 24px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #fff;
      background: linear-gradient(
        165deg,
        rgba(255,255,255,0.12) 0%,
        rgba(255,255,255,0.05) 35%,
        rgba(255,255,255,0.025) 100%
      );
      backdrop-filter: blur(28px) saturate(190%) brightness(1.06);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(28px) saturate(190%) brightness(1.06);
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      box-shadow:
        0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.45),
        inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.14),
        inset 0 -1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: box-shadow 0.5s, transform 0.3s;
    }
    .connect-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow:
        0 12px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.55),
        inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.18),
        inset 0 -1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    }
    .connect-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(
        135deg,
        rgba(59,130,246,0.22) 0%,
        rgba(59,130,246,0.06) 25%,
        rgba(59,130,246,0.02) 50%,
        rgba(59,130,246,0.06) 75%,
        rgba(59,130,246,0.18) 100%
      );
      -webkit-mask: linear-gradient(#fff 0 0) content-box, linear-gradient(#fff 0 0);
      -webkit-mask-composite: xor;
      mask-composite: exclude;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 5;
      opacity: 0.55;
      transition: opacity 0.4s;
    }
    .connect-card:hover::before { opacity: 1; }
    .connect-card svg {
      color: #60A5FA;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }
    .connect-label {
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }
    .connect-sub {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .connect-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
  </style>

</BaseLayout>
